<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6520914>
    dc:description "FIGURE 55. Tenedos luzmarinae sp. n. A–D. Male palp (IAvH-I-3731): A. Prolateral view. B. Retroventral view. C. Ventral view. D. Retrolateral view. E–F. Female epigyne (IAvH-I-3441): E. Ventral view. F. Dorsal view. Scale bars:A–B: 300µm; C–D: 500 µm; E–F: 200µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6520914/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6520918>
    dc:description "FIGURE 56. Tenedos luzmarinae sp. n. A–B. Male palp (IAvH-I-3731): A. Ventral view. B. Retrolateral view. C–D. Female epigyne (IAvH-I-3441): C. Ventral view. D. Dorsal view. Scale bars: A–B: 200µm; C–D: 500µm.Abbreviations:ApC, appendix of the conductor; aMA, anterior branch of the median apophysis; EB, embolus base; E, embolus; FD, fertilization ducts; LB, lateral borders; pMA, posterior branch of the median apophysis; MFP, median field plate; pRTA, posterior branch of retrolateral apophysis; S, spermathecae; SD, spermatic ducts; SR, seminal receptacles; VTA, ventral tegular apophysis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6520918/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6520910>
    dc:description "FIGURE 54. Tenedos luzmarinae sp. n. A–B. Male habitus (IAvH-I-3731): A. Dorsal view. B. Ventral view. C–D. Female habitus (IAvH-I-3441): C. Dorsal view. D. Ventral view. Scale bar: A–D: 2mm." ;
